丹尼爾在2007年的《[[哈利·波特與鳳凰社_(電影)|哈利波特：鳳凰會的密令]]》第5次重演角色，講述他於上一輯電影跟[[佛地魔|佛地魔]]對戰後回到[[霍格華茲|霍格華茲]]。電影舉行了一個記者招待會積極回應記者的提問<ref name="rtscore"/>。IGN的影評人史蒂芬·霍恩（Steven Horn）發現了的是「罕見的是電影內容比原材料還要多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/803/803083p1.html |title=Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix Review |first=Steven |last=Horn |work=IGN |date=2007-07-10 |accessdate=2011-05-29 |archive-date=2012-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120524022424/http://movies.ign.com/articles/803/803083p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>」。《[[每日新聞_(紐約)|紐約每日經濟新聞]]》的[[Colin_Bertram|Colin Bertram]]稱它為系列中最好的電影<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/movies/2007/07/08/2007-07-08_phoenix_hot_for_harry.html |title='Phoenix' hot for Harry |first=Colin |last=Bertram |work=New York Daily News |publisher=Mortimer Zuckerman |date=2007-07-14 |accessdate=2011-05-29 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsV3fMD1?url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/phoenix-hot-harry-article-1.267038 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。丹尼爾稱導演[[大衛·葉斯|大衛·葉斯]]與女演員[[伊梅達·史丹頓|伊梅達·史丹頓]]令電影工作是系列中最有趣的一齣<ref>{{cite news |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/798/798991p1.html |title=Interview with Daniel Radcliffe |work=IGN UK |accessdate=2011-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120505122903/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/798/798991p1.html |archive-date=2012-05-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。而丹尼爾的表現得到多個獎項的提名，並贏得2008年的《[[國家電影獎|國家電影獎]]》的「最佳男演員表現獎」<ref name="nma">{{cite web |url=http://www.nationalmovieawards.com/winners |title=The 2011 NMAs |publisher=[[National_Movie_Awards|National Movie Awards]] |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409081613/http://www.nationalmovieawards.com/winners |archive-date=2016-04-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。由於系列的延續及丹尼爾的名氣，他與[[艾瑪·華森|艾瑪華森]]及[[魯伯特·葛林|魯伯特·葛林]]獲邀在好萊塢的[[格勞曼中國劇院|格勞曼中國劇院]]留下他們的手印、足印及魔杖印記<ref name="grauman">{{cite web |title=Hollywood Blvd Celebrates Potter's 'Wands Of Fame' |publisher=[[CBS|CBS]] |work=[[KCBS-TV|KCBS-TV]] |date=2007-07-09 |url=http://cbs2.com/topstories/local_story_190124828.html |accessdate=2007-07-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927183346/http://cbs2.com/topstories/local_story_190124828.html |archivedate=2007-09-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

