728703p1.html |title=Daniel Radcliffe Signs on to Made For TV Movie |work=IGN |date=2006-08-28 |accessdate=2011-03-31 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVBYP0P?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/08/28/daniel-radcliffe-signs-on-to-made-for-tv-movie |dead-url=no }}</ref>」

