2009年7月發布的《[[哈利·波特與混血王子_(電影)|哈利波特：混血王子的背叛]]》，是電影系列中的第6集。這輯電影確實比上一輯優勝，接連打破了當時在美國最大的午夜場次紀錄，顯示了在3,000間影院放映賺得22,200,000美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1616302/harry-potter-breaks-midnight-records.jhtml |title='Harry Potter And The Half-Blood Prince' Breaks Midnight Records |publisher=MTV |date=2009-07-15 |first=Adam |last=Rosenberg |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2011-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715080636/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1616302/harry-potter-breaks-midnight-records.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且是有史以來英國最大規模的星期三開畫日，1,305個影院中賺得7,600,000美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2604&p=.htm |work=Box Office Mojo |first=Brandon |last=Grey |script-title=en:Sixth ‘Harry Potter’ Posts Franchise-Best Opening Day |date=2009-07-16 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2011-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718072125/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2604&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《混血王子的背叛》共取得933,000,000美元的門票銷售<ref name="thenumbersbo"/>，並於系列中獲得最多影評人正面評價的一齣電影，讚賞電影的故事、方向、攝影、視覺效果及音樂能使人有"情感上的滿足"<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_half_blood_prince/news/1831803/tomatometer_watch_how_good_is_harry_potter_and_the_half-blood_prince/|title=How Good is Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince?|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]]|first=Jen|last=Yamato|accessdate=2011-06-02|archive-date=2014-09-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVCw6s3?url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/harry_potter_and_the_half_blood_prince/news/1831803/tomatometer_watch_how_good_is_harry_potter_and_the_half-blood_prince/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/search/full_search.php?search=harry%20potter |title=Harry Potter |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixster |accessdate=2011-06-02 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVGGULg?url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/search/full_search.php?search=harry%20potter |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/harry-potter-and-the-half-blood-prince |title=Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2011-06-02 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVGRBqu?url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/harry-potter-and-the-half-blood-prince |dead-url=no }}</ref>。丹尼爾憑這齣電影在2010年的[[MTV電影大獎|MTV電影頒獎典禮]]中獲得「最佳男表現獎」及「全球巨星獎」<ref name="mtvma10">{{cite web |url=http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2010/05/12/mtv-movie-awards-2010-nominees-list/ |title=MTV Movie Awards 2010: Full Nominees List! |publisher=MTV |date=2010-05-12 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120223702/http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2010/05/12/mtv-movie-awards-2010-nominees-list |archive-date=2010-11-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

基於電影的財政及劇本的原因，最後一部小說將分拆為兩部電影，以[[背靠背電影製作|背靠背電影製作]]方式拍攝<ref>{{cite news |title=Longer spell at box office for Harry Potter |date=2008-03-14 |first=Jack |last=Malvern |work=The Times }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22200 |title=Potter Producer Talks Deathly Hallows |accessdate=2008-03-14 |date=2008-03-14 |first=Olly |last=Richards |publisher=Bauer Consumer Media |work=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |archive-date=2011-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710192807/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=22200 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，惹來追隨系列書迷的批評。丹尼爾為電影分拆辯護，指不可能把整本小說內容適切的放到只有一齣的電影中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-talks-about-the-deathly-hallows-split |title=Daniel Radcliffe talks about the Deathly Hallows split |work=[[Total_Film|Total Film]] |publisher=Future Publishing Limited |date=2011-05-09 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVNwl3N?url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-talks-about-the-deathly-hallows-split |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他補充說，最後一部電影的節奏是非常快，動作也很多，而上集會更穩重，集中在角色的發展，再補充說，他們把那些東西結合，那些東西不會在最後剪接中得到的<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-differences-deathly-hallow-48562 |first=Kimberly |last=Nordyke |title=Daniel Radcliffe on the Differences Between 'Deathly Hallow' Parts 1 and 2 |work=Hollywood Reporter |date=2010-11-26 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVQ7Iet?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-differences-deathly-hallow-48562 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

