《[[哈利·波特與死神的聖物_(電影)|哈利波特：死神的聖物(上)]]》在2010年發布，劇情講述哈利、榮恩及妙麗離開[[霍格華茲|霍格華茲]]，追蹤[[佛地魔|佛地魔]]的分靈體，佛地魔用以分開身體與靈魂的東西。電影於2010年11月發布，美國的電影票房收入超過950,000,000美元<ref name="thenumbersbo">{{cite web |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/people/DRADC.php |title=Daniel Radcliffe |work=The-Numbers.com |publisher=Nash Information Services, LLC |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2011-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110807083053/http://www.the-numbers.com/people/DRADC.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影最賺錢的地方是英國，據報是歷史上開畫連續三天的最高票房紀錄，在91個市場中賺得205,000,000美元，令它成為有史以來非美國非夏季開畫的最賣座電影，並成為「第四齣最賣座的全球開畫」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2992&p=.htm |first=Ray |last=Subers |title=Around-the-World Roundup: 'Deathly Hallows' Scores Top Non-Summer Opening Ever |work=Box Office Mojo |date=2010-11-21 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2011-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719175106/http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2992&p=.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影收到大部分媒體的好評<ref name="rtscore">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/daniel_radcliffe/ |title=Daniel Radcliffe |work=Rotten Tomatoes |publisher=Flixster |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsUrTkbf?url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/daniel_radcliffe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[File:Daniel_Radcliffe,_Emma_Watson_&_Rupert_Grint_colour.jpg|230px]]及[[魯伯特·葛林|魯伯特·葛林]]出席《哈利波特：死神的聖物(下)》於[[倫敦|倫敦]]的首映。]]

系列中最後一輯電影，《[[哈利·波特與死神的聖物_(電影)|哈利波特：死神的聖物(下)]]》，在[[澳洲|澳洲]]於2011年7月13日開始，進行全球發布。電影講述他們在[[霍格華茲|霍格華茲]]與[[佛地魔|佛地魔]]的追隨者對抗，及哈利波特與佛地魔的終極對決。丹尼爾與電影都大受好評<ref name="rtscore"/>。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的Ann Hornaday問：「誰能預料得到丹尼爾、[[艾瑪·華森|艾瑪]]及[[魯伯特·格林特|魯伯特·格林特]]會成為好演員嗎？<ref>{{cite news|last=Hornaday|first=Ann|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/gog/movies/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2,1158848/critic-review.html|title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows{{spaced ndash}}Part 2|work=The Washington Post|date=2011-07-13|accessdate=2011-09-04|archive-date=2014-09-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVc524z?url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/gog/movies/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2,1158848.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>」；同樣地，Rex Reed說：「坦白地說，我很遺憾看到丹尼爾走出去<ref>{{cite web|last=Reed|first=Rex|url=http://www.observer.com/2011/07/harry-potter-saga-comes-to-a-thrilling-end-in-the-final-film/|title=Harry Potter Saga Come to Thrilling End in Final Film|work=New York Observer|date=2011-07-12|accessdate=2011-09-04|archive-date=2011-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830214747/http://www.observer.com/2011/07/harry-potter-saga-comes-to-a-thrilling-end-in-the-final-film/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」；而《[[滾石雜誌|滾石雜誌]]》的評論者Peter Travers評價丹尼爾：「先生，演得好。<ref>{{cite web|last=Travers|first=Peter|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-20110713|title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows, Part 2|work=Rolling Stone|date=2011-07-13|accessdate=2011-09-04|archive-date=2014-09-26|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVct2ds?url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/harry-potter-and-the-deathly-hallows-part-2-20110713|dead-url=no}}</ref>」當中都不乏批評，Roger Ebert說丹尼爾、愛瑪和路拔都是「被配角搶鏡了<ref>{{cite web|last=Ebert|first=Roger|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20110713/REVIEWS/110719994/-1/RSS|title=Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2 (PG-13)|work=Chicago Sun-Times|date=2011-07-13|accessdate=2011-09-04|archive-date=2011-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110913091448/http://www.rogerebert.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20110713%2FREVIEWS%2F110719994%2F-1%2FRSS|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。

電影打破了票房紀錄，包括最大的午夜發布<ref name='firstday'>{{cite web|last=Gray|first=Brandon|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3210&p=.htm|title='Harry Potter' Conjures Opening Day Record|publisher=Box Office Mojo|date=2011-07-16|accessdate=2011-09-04|archive-date=2011-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901231014/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3210&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，及最大的發布周末<ref>{{cite web|last=Gray|first=Brandon|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3211&p=.htm|title=Weekend Report: 'Harry' Makes History|publisher=Box Office Mojo|date=2011-07-18|accessdate=2011-09-04|archive-date=2011-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831020948/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3211&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《哈利波特：死神的聖物(下)》是目前所有時間最高票房紀錄的第四位，第二位的是全球票房超過1.3億的[[詹姆斯·卡梅倫|詹姆斯·卡梅倫]]的電影，而首位的是電影《[[復仇者聯盟_(電影)|復仇者聯盟]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/|title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2011-09-04|archive-date=2001-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010716094602/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。丹尼爾承認，有些人不能將他與哈利波特這個角色分開，但他也說自己"永遠跟這個系列電影有關聯而感到自豪<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-thinks-harry-will-stick-to-me |title=Daniel Radcliffe: 'Harry Potter will stick to me' |work=[[Total_Film|Total Film]] |publisher=Future Publishing Limited |first=Josh |last=Winning |date=2010-11-18 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsVePuFW?url=http://www.totalfilm.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-thinks-harry-will-stick-to-me |dead-url=no }}</ref>"。儘管對這部電影有很多正面的感受，但丹尼爾沒有興趣再做更多「哈利波特」電影。在[[羅琳|羅琳]]暗示她正在寫第８部作品後，他被問及是否會演出其他系列時說：「我認為這是很值得難以預測的，我覺得在一個角色花上10年是一個很長的時間。<ref>{{cite news |title=Boy Wizard Says No More Harry Potter |work=Sky News |publisher=British Sky Broadcasting |date=2010-11-10 |first=Lisa |last=Dowd}}</ref>」儘管在整個電影系列中花了這麼長的時間，丹尼爾稱他沒有像其他小演員那樣錯過他的童年，他說：「我演波特的時候已經有更好的生活展望<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.timeout.com/film/features/show-feature/8221/daniel-radcliffe-interview.html |first=Dave |last=Calhoun |title=Daniel Radcliffe: interview |work=[[Time_Out_(company)|Time Out]] |publisher=Time Out Group Ltd |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018182227/http://www.timeout.com/film/features/show-feature/8221/daniel-radcliffe-interview.html |archive-date=2012-10-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>」。拍攝歷時一年的時間，於2010年6月結束，在拍攝的最後一天，丹尼爾面對著大部分的演員及拍攝團隊公開地哭了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1641985/daniel-radcliffe-recalls-weeping-during-final-harry-potter-shoot.jhtml |first=Eric |last=Ditzian |title=Daniel Radcliffe Recalls 'Weeping' During Final 'Harry Potter' Shoot |publisher=MTV |date=2010-06-21 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |archive-date=2011-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110529170321/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1641985/daniel-radcliffe-recalls-weeping-during-final-harry-potter-shoot.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

