== 個人生活 ==
2005年，丹尼爾16歲的時候，[[國家肖像館|英國國家肖像畫廊]]擺放著丹尼爾的個人畫像，成為英國有史以來最年輕的、在NPG擁有個人肖像的非皇室成員。

2006年4月13日，[[斯圖亞特·皮爾森·萊特|斯圖亞特·皮爾森·萊特]]所畫的丹尼爾個人畫像在[[皇家國立劇院|皇家國立劇院]]的新展覽開幕作首次亮相，畫像其後移至NPG擺放<ref name="portrait">{{cite web |title=Daniel Radcliffe drawing acquired by National Portrait Gallery |publisher=National Portrait Gallery |date=2006-04-11 |url=http://www.npg.org.uk/live/prelharrypotter.asp |accessdate=2007-06-05 |archive-date=2007-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070523003133/http://www.npg.org.uk/live/prelharrypotter.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年，丹尼爾透露自己患有輕度的神經系統疾病 - [[動作協調能力喪失症|動作協調能力喪失症]]，動作協調能力障礙有時會變得很差，使他即使讀書寫字替自己綁上鞋帶也無法完成，丹尼爾說「我在學校有一段很困難的時候，所有東西都是廢話，我沒有可以識別的天賦才能<ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Health/story?id=5605093&page=1 |title=Dyspraxia Explains Harry Potter's Klutziness |first=Emily |last=Friedman |work=ABC News |publisher=American Broadcasting Company |date=2008-08-19 |accessdate=2011-05-26 |archive-date=2011-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110214123953/http://abcnews.go.com/Health/story?id=5605093&page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 」。

2010年8月，丹尼爾發現自己過於依賴酒精，於是戒掉喝酒習慣<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/8614366/Daniel-Radcliffe-why-I-dont-drink-alcohol-any-more.html |title=Daniel Radcliffe: why I don't drink alcohol any more |first=Anita |last=Singh |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=2011-07-04 |accessdate=2011-07-04 |location=London |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsW148MD?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/8614366/Daniel-Radcliffe-why-I-dont-drink-alcohol-any-more.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年，丹尼爾表示，「我認為自己是猶太人及愛爾蘭人，儘管我事實上是英國人<ref name="Parade (2012-01-07)"/>。」他還說，「我是個[[無神論者|無神論者]]，當宗教開始影響立法的時候，我會是個激進的無神論者<ref>{{cite web |author=Final |url=http://tvnz.co.nz/entertainment-news/daniel-radcliffe-militant-atheist-4717220 |title=Daniel Radcliffe - militant atheist |work=Television New Zealand |publisher=TVNZ |date=2012-02-12 |accessdate=2012-06-13 |archive-date=2012-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528084956/http://tvnz.co.nz/entertainment-news/daniel-radcliffe-militant-atheist-4717220 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。」他並且為自己作為猶太人而感到自豪<ref name="dailybeast">{{cite web|last=Sessums|first=Kevin|title=Dirty Harry|publisher=The Newsweek Daily Beast Company|work=The Daily Beast|date=2009-01-26|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/dirty-harry|accessdate=2018-05-23|quote=Daniel Radcliffe: "My dad is Northern Irish and my mum is Jewish. That’s working blood. Though I am not religious in the least, I am very proud to be Jewish."|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517211131/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2009/01/26/dirty-harry.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Singh |first=Anita |title=Daniel Radcliffe: a cool nerd |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/5734000/Daniel-Radcliffe-a-cool-nerd.html |work=The Daily Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |date=2009-06-04 |accessdate=2009-06-06 |location=London |archive-date=2009-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090706021225/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/5734000/Daniel-Radcliffe-a-cool-nerd.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dantheman">{{cite news |last=McLean |first=Craig |title=Dan the Man |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2009/jul/04/daniel-radcliffe-harry-potter-jk-rowling |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian News and Media Limited |date=2009-07-04 |accessdate=2009-07-11 |location=London |archive-date=2012-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229200317/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2009/jul/04/daniel-radcliffe-harry-potter-jk-rowling |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

丹尼爾一直是[[英國工黨|英國工黨]]的支持者<ref name="quinn1">{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/feb/06/daniel-radcliffe-ends-lib-dem-support | location=London | work=The Guardian | first=Ben | last=Quinn | title=Daniel Radcliffe ends support for Liberal Democrats | date=2012-02-06 | accessdate=2012-09-07 | archive-date=2012-06-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618105715/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/feb/06/daniel-radcliffe-ends-lib-dem-support | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在[[2010年英國大選|2010年英國大選]]之前，他表示贊同[[自由民主黨_(英國)|自由民主黨]]領袖[[尼克·克萊格|尼克·克萊格]]的政見，他公開地支持英國自由民主黨<ref name="libdem">{{cite web |url=http://blog.moviefone.com/2010/03/24/daniel-radcliffe-pledges-support-for-the-liberal-democrats/ |first=Pete |last=Stanton |title=Daniel Radcliffe Pledges Support for the Liberal Democrats |work=Moviefone |publisher=AOL Inc |date=2010-03-24 |accessdate=2011-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120803093426/http://blog.moviefone.com/2010/03/24/daniel-radcliffe-pledges-support-for-the-liberal-democrats/ |archive-date=2012-08-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。然而在2012年，丹尼爾轉向效忠英國工黨領袖[[文立彬|文立彬]]<ref name="quinn1"/>，原因是他對尼克·克萊格及英國自由民主黨在[[卡梅倫內閣|2010年英國聯合政府]]的表現感到失望。

興趣方面，丹尼爾是[[地下音樂|地下音樂]]<ref name="tomfeltonfriend">{{cite news |title=Harry Potter Y EL MISTERIO DEL PRINCIPE |publisher=Cinemanía |date=July 2009}}</ref>和[[朋克搖滾|朋克搖滾]]<ref>{{harvnb|Norwich|2005|pp=120–121}}</ref><ref name="favband">{{cite web |title=Harry Potter reveals his favourite band |work=NME |date=2007-07-20}}</ref>的支持者，同時他熱衷於板球運動，包括板球運動員[[沙奇·德魯卡|沙奇·德魯卡]]的追隨者<ref name="cricket1">{{cite news |last=Pidd |first=Helen |title='If the script says have sex, I have sex' |publisher=Guardian News and Media Limited |work=The Guardian |date=2007-09-07 |url=http://arts.guardian.co.uk/filmandmusic/story/0,,2163370,00.html |accessdate=2007-09-07 |location=London |archive-date=2007-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070913142825/http://arts.guardian.co.uk/filmandmusic/story/0,,2163370,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/Daniel-Radcliffe-is-a-huge-Sachin-fan/Article1-721526.aspx|title=Daniel Radcliffe is a huge Sachin fan|date=2011-07-15|last=Bansal|first=Robin|accessdate=2011-09-24|newspaper=Hindustan Times|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110904043651/http://www.hindustantimes.com/Daniel-Radcliffe-is-a-huge-Sachin-fan/Article1-721526.aspx|archive-date=2011-09-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

他對寫短篇小說及詩歌也有一種熱情<ref name="otherauthorname"/>。2007年11月，丹尼爾以筆名Jacob Gershon（以他中間的名字與他母親猶太版本的娘家姓氏）在地下時尚雜誌《Rubbish》發表了幾首詩<ref name="dantheman"/><ref name="otherauthorname">{{cite news |title=Harry Potter actor Daniel Radcliffe's 'secret life as a published poet' |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/5799717/Harry-Potter-actor-Daniel-Radcliffes-secret-life-as-a-published-poet.html |work=The Daily Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |date=2009-07-11 |accessdate=2011-05-26 |location=London |archive-date=2017-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731165220/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/5799717/Harry-Potter-actor-Daniel-Radcliffes-secret-life-as-a-published-poet.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

丹尼爾很享受跟《哈利波特》的同伴 - 飾演馬份的[[湯姆·費爾頓|湯姆·費爾頓]]<ref name="tomfeltonfriend"/><ref>{{cite episode|serieslink=Friday Night with Jonathan Ross|series=Friday Night with Jonathan Ross|title=Emma Watson |url=|network=BBC One|airdate=5 July 2009|seriesno=16|number=22|minutes=7:40–19:40}}</ref>的友誼，他們並跟丹尼爾的家人緊密團結，他歸功於他們保持他的立場<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/2675435/Daniel-Radcliffe-I-lost-my-virginity-to-an-older-woman.html |title=Daniel Radcliffe: I lost my virginity to an older woman |first=Anita |last=Singh |work=The Daily Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |date=2008-09-03 |accessdate=2011-05-28 |location=London |archive-date=2011-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110317040100/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/2675435/Daniel-Radcliffe-I-lost-my-virginity-to-an-older-woman.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

談到[[同性戀恐懼|同性戀恐懼]]，丹尼爾在2009年開始為[[特雷弗爾計劃|特雷弗爾計劃]]拍攝[[公共服務宣傳|公共服務宣傳]]片，推廣預防同性戀青少年自殺的意識<ref name="ttp2">{{cite news |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-receive-trevor-projects-169548 |title=Daniel Radcliffe to Receive Trevor Project's Hero Award |first=Lindsay |last=Powers |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2011-03-21 |accessdate=2011-05-26 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsW6av3H?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/daniel-radcliffe-receive-trevor-projects-169548 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ttp">{{cite news |url=http://articles.nydailynews.com/2010-02-27/gossip/27057364_1_suicide-prevention-gay-men-attempts-suicide |title=Daniel Radcliffe films Trevor Project suicide prevention public service announcement for gay youth |work=New York Daily News |publisher=[[Mortimer_Zuckerman|Mortimer Zuckerman]] |date=2010-02-27 |accessdate=2011-05-26 |archive-date=2014-09-26 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6SsW49PPV?url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/daniel-radcliffe-films-trevor-project-suicide-prevention-public-service-announcement-gay-youth-article-1.178410 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他首次了解到該會的工作是於2008年的百老匯舞台劇《戀馬狂》<ref name="ttp"/>並在財政人作出捐助<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thetrevorproject.org/news/daniel-radcliffe-makes-major-donation-support-trevor-project |title=DANIEL RADCLIFFE MAKES MAJOR DONATION TO SUPPORT THE TREVOR PROJECT |publisher=The Trevor Project |date=2009-08-10 |accessdate=2011-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130801205554/http://www.thetrevorproject.org/news/daniel-radcliffe-makes-major-donation-support-trevor-project |archive-date=2013-08-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他在2010年的一個訪問中表示：「我很討厭那些對男同性戀者和女同性戀者及雙性戀者沒有包容的人，現在我能夠提供真正幫助或為這件事做點事，我感到自己在非常幸運的位置上。」於同一個訪問中，他亦說到公眾人物倡導平等權利的重要性<ref name="ttp"/>。他認為參與這些事是他職業生涯中最重要的事情之一<ref name="ttp2"/>。對於他在組織中的工作，他獲頒「英雄獎2011」。

根據報導，丹尼爾出演首部《哈利波特》電影已賺得1,000,000英鎊<ref name="maincastinter"/>，並在第六集賺得15,000,000英鎊<ref name="Parade (2009-06-28)"/>，但來源均不同意於他的個人財富。他出現於[[星期日泰晤士報2006年富豪榜|星期日泰晤士報2006年富豪榜]]中，估計他的個人財富達到14,000,000英鎊，使他成為[[英國|英國]]最富裕的年輕人之一<ref name="fortune">{{cite news |title=Daniel Radcliffe|work=The Times |year=2006 |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/richlist/person/0,,39471,00.html |accessdate=2011-05-31 |location=London |first1=Sam |last1=Coates |first2=Anushka |last2=Asthana}}</ref>。在2009年3月，他在[[富比士|富比士]]的「最有價值年輕明星排行榜」中排列第一<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/2009/03/10/teen-star-currency-business-media-forbes-star-currency_slide_2.html |title=In Pictures: Hollywood's Most Valuable Young Stars |date=2009-03-10 |first=John |last=Burman |work=Forbes |publisher=Forbes.com LLC |accessdate=2011-05-27 |archive-date=2011-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720191931/http://www.forbes.com/2009/03/10/teen-star-currency-business-media-forbes-star-currency_slide_2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在4月[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]量度他的淨資產為30,000,000英鎊，成為了英國第12位最富有的年輕人<ref name='70m'>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/5224902/Harry-Potter-magic-puts-Daniel-Radcliffe-12th-on-young-Rich-List.html |title=Harry Potter magic puts Daniel Radcliffe 12th on young Rich List |accessdate=2011-05-26 |first=Sarah |last=Knapton |date=2009-04-27 |work=The Daily Telegraph |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |location=London |archive-date=2018-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180218115227/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/5224902/Harry-Potter-magic-puts-Daniel-Radcliffe-12th-on-young-Rich-List.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在2009年末的時候，丹尼爾成為了最富有的少年人<ref name="Parade (2009-06-28)"/>。

2010年2月，丹尼爾成為好萊塢最高薪酬男影星<ref name="earnings 2010">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/8500494.stm|title=Harry Potter star Emma Watson is top-earning actress|date=2010-02-05|publisher=BBC|work=BBC News|accessdate=2011-05-27|archive-date=2014-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140516123732/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/8500494.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並以78,000,000英鎊位列《[[富比士|富比士]]》12月好萊塢最高薪酬演員名單的第五位，<ref group="note">指他們出現於電影中所牽涉的金額，並非他們的個人收入</ref>（主要因為《[[哈利·波特与死亡圣器（下）|哈利·波特-死神的聖物]]》於該年上映）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/2010/12/20/highest-grossing-actors-2010-business-entertainment_slide_6.html |title=In Pictures: Hollywood's Highest-Grossing Actors |work=Forbes |publisher=Forbes.com LLC |date=2010-12-20 |accessdate=2011-05-27 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120730155640/http://www.forbes.com/2010/12/20/highest-grossing-actors-2010-business-entertainment_slide_6.html |archivedate=2012-07-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管之前有預測指丹尼爾在《哈利波特》系列電影總共已累積70,000,000英磅收入時<ref name='70m'/>，據報導他是僅在2010年賺得£28,500,000英鎊的演員，這使他比[[威廉王子|威廉王子]]及[[哈利王子|哈利王子]]更富有<ref>{{cite news |title=Now that's magic: Harry Potter star doubles his wealth to £28.5m in just a year |work=Daily Mail |location=UK |publisher=Associated Newspapers Ltd |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1321246/Now-thats-magic-Harry-Potter-star-doubles-wealth-28-5m-just-year.html |date=2010-10-16 |accessdate=2011-05-27 |archive-date=2011-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110801052901/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1321246/Now-thats-magic-Harry-Potter-star-doubles-wealth-28-5m-just-year.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管他擁有很多財富，丹尼爾說他並沒有提升自己的口味，他主要的支出都是用來購買書籍，他說：「我看很多書的<ref>{{Cite news |last=Maddocks |first=Fiona |title=From Harry to hunk |publisher=[[London_Evening_Standard|London Evening Standard]] |date=2007-02-02 |url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/film/article-23384050-from-harry-to-hunk.do |accessdate=2010-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101120004039/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/film/article-23384050-from-harry-to-hunk.do |archive-date=2010-11-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。」他還表示金錢永遠不是他生活的重點<ref name="Parade (2009-06-28)"/>。

2012年1月，丹尼爾說他跟製片助理Rosie Coker關係發展中，2014年4月，公開已與大自己5歲的女演員Erin Darke交往2年<ref name="dailymail">Bull, Sarah. [http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2094162/Daniel-Radcliffe-girlfriend-Rosie-Coker-Shes-far-good-me.html Daniel Radcliffe on girlfriend Rosie Coker: 'She's far too good for me!' | Mail Online] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2094162/Daniel-Radcliffe-girlfriend-Rosie-Coker-Shes-far-good-me.html |date=20130605223702 }}. 31 January 2012. Retrieved 6 February 2012.</ref>。

